  "title": "⭐ AI Engineer",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Research, design, and develop computer and network software or specialised utility programs.</li>\n  <li>Analyse user needs and develop software solutions, applying principles and techniques of computer science, engineering, and mathematical analysis.</li>\n  <li>Update software, enhance existing software capabilities, and develop and direct software testing and validation procedures.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with hardware/infrastructure engineers to integrate hardware and software systems, developing specifications and performance requirements.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>A Bachelor's degree in Computer Science.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years' work experience as a Software Engineer/Developer.</li>\n  <li>Able to communicate with Chinese-speaking clients.</li>\n  <li>Willing to meet the tight timeline delivery.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Invest In Your Future With IP-Tribe</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>IP-Tribe is more than just a workplace; it's a community where you can make a real impact and grow your career. We offer a comprehensive package designed to support your success:</li>\n  <li>We offer competitive salaries to commensurate with your experience and expertise.</li>\n  <li>Take advantage of our health and wellness programs, designed to keep you at your best.</li>\n  <li>Enjoy generous annual leave and flexible work arrangements, giving you the freedom to recharge and pursue your passions.</li>\n  <li>Join a collaborative and supportive team culture, where your voice is heard and your contributions are valued.</li>\n  <li>Unlock your potential with clear opportunities for career progression and growth within our expanding organisation.</li>\n</ul>",
